TITLE: Extended Search with Operators in Fuse.js
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the extended search feature with various operators like fuzzy matching, exact matching, prefix/suffix matching, and the use of AND/OR operators to create complex search patterns.
SOURCE: https://github.com/krisk/fuse/blob/main/docs/examples.md#2025-04-17_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
