LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const options = {
  includeScore: true,
  useExtendedSearch: true,
  keys: ['title']
}

const fuse = new Fuse(books, options)

// Search for items that include "Man" and "Old",
// OR end with "Artist"
fuse.search("'Man 'Old | Artist$")
```

