TITLE: Example $and Query in Fuse.js
DESCRIPTION: Shows a practical example of using the $and operator to search for entries matching both author and title criteria.
SOURCE: https://github.com/krisk/fuse/blob/main/docs/api/query.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const result = fuse.search({
  $and: [{ author: 'abc' }, { title: 'xyz' }]
})
```

