TITLE: Querying Dotted Keys in Fuse.js
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to configure Fuse.js options and construct queries for searching through nested objects with dotted keys using $path and $val properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/krisk/fuse/blob/main/docs/api/query.md#2025-04-17_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const options = {
  useExtendedSearch: true,
  includeScore: true,
  keys: [
    'title',
    ['author', 'first.name'],
    ['author', 'last.name'],
    'author.age'
  ]
}

const query = {
  $and: [
    {
      $path: ['author', 'first.name'],
      $val: 'jon'
    },
    {
      $path: ['author', 'last.name'],
      $val: 'scazi'
    }
  ]
}
```

