TITLE: Extended Search with Logical Operators
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates combining logical operators with extended search features including fuzzy matching, exact matching, and prefix matching.
SOURCE: https://github.com/krisk/fuse/blob/main/docs/api/query.md#2025-04-17_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const result = fuse.search({
  $and: [
    { title: 'old war' }, // Fuzzy "old war"
    { color: "'blue" }, // Exact match for blue
    {
      $or: [
        { title: '^lock' }, // Starts with "lock"
        { title: '!arts' } // Does not have "arts"
      ]
    }
  ]
})
```

