TITLE: Default Weight Configuration in Fuse.js
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how default weight values are assigned when not explicitly specified. When weights are not provided, they default to 1, while Fuse.js normalizes all weights internally.
SOURCE: https://github.com/krisk/fuse/blob/main/docs/examples.md#2025-04-17_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
